Aussie Walkabout Wine Gift Trio
List.Description:
This taste of Australia consists of three classic, value-driven Australian wines: Shoofly Shiraz, Plantagenet Hazard Hill Sauvignon Blanc/Semillon and d'Arenberg Stump Jump Cabernet Sauvignon. This one's a beauty!

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Shoofly Shiraz
    The Shoofly Shiraz shows earthy gravel, spicy licorice and dense, dark mulberries. The vibrant red fruit runs the length of the palate and lingers with a "have another glass" finish.

  • Plantagenet Hazard Hill Sauvignon Blanc/Semillon
    In this lively Bordeaux-style white blend, Semillon's lemon character is lifted and complemented by the grassy gooseberry notes of Sauvignon Blanc and the palate weight of Semillon is enhanced by the Sauvignon Blanc's tighter linear structure.

  • d'Arenberg Stump Jump Cabernet Sauvignon
    Youthful and fresh, the palate has a lovely leafy berry core than runs the whole way through to a lovely finish of fine mineral tannins. The oak is totally integrated and allows the fruit characters to star.

  • Printed insert that describes the featured wines

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.
